✅ **4 Random Jokes** - Click the button to see a different joke each time
✅ **Responsive Design** - Works on mobile and desktop
✅ **Beautiful UI** - Gradient background and smooth animations
✅ **Easy to Customize** - Simply add more jokes to the `jokes` array

